trans-unit.source: Implements the interfaces of an ActiveX site for use as a base class by the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.WebBrowserSite?displayProperty=fullName> class.
trans-unit.target: Implementerer grensesnitt for et ActiveX-område for bruk som en basisklasse av den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.WebBrowserSite?displayProperty=fullName> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Releases all resources used by the <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowserSiteBase"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Frigir alle ressursene som brukes av den <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowserSiteBase"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Releases the unmanaged resources used by the <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowserSiteBase"></xref> and optionally releases the managed resources.
trans-unit.target: Frigir uforvaltede ressursene som brukes av den <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowserSiteBase"> </xref> og eventuelt frigir administrerte ressurser.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> to release both managed and unmanaged resources; <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref> to release only unmanaged resources.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>å frigjøre både administrerte og uforvaltede ressurser. <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref> frigi bare uforvaltede ressurser.
